  "format": "Sean Fennessey and Mallory Rubin record a full-spoiler emergency deep dive the day after a Tuesday-morning screening of 'Avengers: Endgame': the time-travel rules, the deaths of Tony Stark and Black Widow, Captain America's send-off, then each host's five favorite Marvel movies and a look at what comes next.",
